.9, "evidence": "it’d be Richie Havens and then Cream and then Tim and then Big Brother and the Holding Company with Janis. Things like that. I played with opposite, or knew all the people on that scene.", "doc_title": "Warren Bernhardt interviewed by Monk Rowe, Bearsville, New York, January 3, 2012", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/warren-bernhardt-interviewed-monk-rowe-bearsville-new-york-january-3-2012"}, {"speaker": "David Spinozza", "relation": "has met", "confidence": 0.9, "evidence": "And Richie was getting nervous... I didn't know what to say to Richie... That was a strange session.", "doc_title": "David Spinozza interviewed by Monk Rowe, New Hartford, NY, September 27, 2025", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/david-spinozza-interviewed-monk-rowe-new-hartford-ny-september-27-2025"}]}